{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So most of them were gone the next day, the ones that I had been around with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "This guy that I had been with, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so we went back into the camp again, because we had the [INAUDIBLE] guy with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they were meeting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were going on the tours with their photographers, with their Signal Corps photographers, taking their pictures and talking to these other generals, medical officers, whatever, about what could be done.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they had to report back to Eisenhower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the rest of the time, the day, day and a half, two days, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The smell was, I mean I just hated to go back in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no reason to go back in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could have sit in the airplane.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We get to-- but I was getting schizy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I was getting schizy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was thinking and talking to some of the other guys, you know, Jesus, using really bad, you know, the f-word and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and we all were pretty b-- and we just didn't want to-- we would almost force ourselves to go back and-- and-- we wanted to try to find somebody we could talk to.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did find some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found some people who could speak English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the things that one of the guys was wanted to find out how the hell that gas chamber worked.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't find any water pipes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody said, hey, there's no water pipes to that damn gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, if-- if that's a shower there has to be a source of water to go in there, or what's the point of having a shower with no water pipes?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there weren't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
